          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where we ship",
            "content": "<p>We currently ship anywhere in the contiguous United States. We’re working on Alaska, Hawaii, and international shipping. If you’d like to be notified when we expand, drop your address into our waitlist on the homepage.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_LA3bgx": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping options and costs",
            "content": "<p>We keep this simple:</p><ul><li><strong>Standard shipping (3–5 business days)</strong> — [$X] flat rate, free on orders over [$Y] and on every subscription order.</li><li><strong>Expedited shipping (2 business days)</strong> — [$X] flat rate, available at checkout.</li></ul><p><em>*Drafting note: Replace bracketed amounts with the rates Zaid’s team configures in Shopify. Free shipping for subscriptions is recommended given subscription is the business model — confirm with finance before going live.</em></p><p>Orders ship Monday through Friday, excluding U.S. holidays. Orders placed after 12:00 PM PT typically ship the next business day.</p>"
