        "content_hzgdaE": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tracking",
            "content": "<p>Once your order ships, you’ll get an email with a tracking link. You can also see tracking information in your account.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_CDWMTQ": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Subscriptions",
            "content": "<p>Subscription orders ship at the cadence you choose — every 30 days for the 30/month plan, every 30 days (with four 15-packs) for the 60/month plan. We send a reminder email a few days before each shipment so you can skip, swap, or update your address. Changes need to be made before the renewal processes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_jPBq6a": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "If something goes wrong in transit",
            "content": "<p>Once a package leaves us, the carrier owns it. That said, we’re not going to leave you hanging if it gets lost or arrives damaged. Email hello@tonique.com within 14 days of the delivery date with your order number and a photo (for damage), and we’ll replace the order or refund you.</p><p>Two notes:</p><ul><li>If tracking shows your package was delivered but you can’t find it, please check with neighbors and your building first, then file a claim with the carrier. We’re happy to help, but stolen-from-porch claims need to start with the carrier.</li><li>If an address is entered incorrectly and the package is returned to us, we’ll reach out to confirm the correct address. Reshipping costs may apply.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
